How to have a ZeroNet Customised Domain.description:
In this video I will show you how to customise your ZeroNet domain name, I will not be using NameCoin but will be using a Bitcoin Vanity generator to have a custom start to our Bitcoin public key. In this video I showed me using this vanity gen to create a domain that was used to host a simple website that displays a random Lenny face.

By: Ace Lewis (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRn4xTmE0IIEPsdt6R0gzcw)
